n唔識吹水</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n求包養 一齊去深圳玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我都係<br />\n收入增加但生活方式無變<br />\n日常洗費都係同以前一樣<br />\n( 無你咁揾多 )<br />\n<br />\n不過如果一次半次支岀<br />\n例如旅行/食餐好 會捨得洗<br />\n以前就無資格放蹤呢一次半次"},{"pid":"752fc356e119d8d1eac0d19e643f1eef11ddb25f","tid":102831,"uid":17492,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-03T22:19:45.000Z","msg":"搵緊兩皮鬆d<br />\n最少每個月可以儲下錢 想食咩都唔洗諗咁多<br />\n果d話冇分別 係你突然有需要果時就知"},{"pid":"da7024281ef718470dc0c1d3980c1498209e3902","tid":102831,"uid":55851,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-03T23:21:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>得果10皮有咩用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n供一層君臨天下，養架LaFerrari都已經唔夠用啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n養你老母咩 買到Laferrari 先講喇</blockquote><br />\nching咩事呀你，講咩老母呀"},{"pid":"d95cdc241c5919ce801caf8e98b37309d9d7f4ba","tid":102831,"uid":5649,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-03T23:51:22.000Z","msg":"岩岩fg搵緊1m咋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我寧願做到死下死下<br />\n起碼夠錢用"},{"pid":"953f92f6fdb99203e33059fe053e4b8c95c05a02","tid":102831,"uid":40842,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-04T05:55:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>岩岩fg搵緊1m咋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我寧願做到死下死下<br />\n起碼夠錢用</blockquote><br />\n百萬富翁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a8e3524619ae40bfe3807d1f005cd8e9d5cf648d","tid":102831,"uid":23833,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-06T09:44:41.000Z","msg":"成班撚樣根本唔知10皮一個月份工會點？9 hea行行企企 等出糧？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5f29ab45c732b0993e9b29b6a32c993a6baf7969","tid":102831,"uid":67280,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-06T14:02:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><br />\nOn9<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 生活質素差唔多都講得出，搵10皮一個月你已經唔會有任何錢銀煩惱先</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n10皮一個月就無錢銀煩惱<br />\n咁你生活幾簡單<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你講下會有咩煩惱先啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 減晒啲開支家用供車供樓我諗個個月都仲有幾皮比你吃喝玩樂，但如果你話你要供遊艇供飛機既咁我就收收皮先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n工作壓力<br />\n點樣保住份工同地位<br />\n<br />\n已經夠煩喇掛？<br />\n<br />\n未計應酬老細同客</blockquote><br />\n最多煩工作，就算比人炒左，之後我個個月十皮人工，當你所有支出3，4皮，仲有6，7皮草，咁樣仲唔夠，我屌你老母。你咁撚偉大，叫你老細比返3，4皮你一個月lo，睇撚死你肯定劈炮唔撈<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，十皮野又點，成個屈雞蟲咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7027207d218f3fb9af70825d92a723c865b5c852","tid":102831,"uid":67280,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-06T14:05:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><br />\n<br />\n10皮一個月就無錢銀煩惱<br />\n咁你生活幾簡單<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你講下會有咩煩惱先啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 減晒啲開支家用供車供樓我諗個個月都仲有幾皮比你吃喝玩樂，但如果你話你要供遊艇供飛機既咁我就收收皮先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n搵十萬同搵兩萬比同樣家用?<br />\n搵十萬交稅又同搵兩萬一樣?<br />\n供車供樓前唔使比錢買?<br />\n減晒啲開支家用供車供樓有錢剩就要用晒佢唔儲錢?</blockquote><br />\n明唔明咩叫錢銀煩惱呀，係個個月唔夠錢用個啲先叫錢銀煩惱，你搵十皮一個月，普通市區樓萬8蚊租，家用比夠萬5，一個月一萬基本開支，都仲有成5皮，你用黎玩又得儲又得，當你一個月玩夠一萬，都儲到4皮一個月，你同我講你會有煩惱？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n當佢扣埋稅，1皮啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d5c6bfa73aeab7385a809f4e7324d2c182aaed7d","tid":102831,"uid":67280,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-06T14:07:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>On9<br />\n講到得十萬有工作壓力，兩萬無壓力咁<br />\n你有十萬，已經可以好輕鬆做到好多嘢<br />\n<br />\n兩萬永遠無可能買到樓<br />\n食飯都係麥記譚仔<br />\n去旅行都要窮游<br />\n<br />\n你有十萬，你洗費大<br />\n係你自己選擇</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n十萬同二萬 工作壓力一樣？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n咪玩啦師兄<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n收入大就支出自然大<br />\n你唔好同我講你搵十萬 但洗費同一般打工仔一樣？<br />\n<br />\n不過就算搵2萬都唔一定係窮遊m記譚仔既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n請解釋點解人工高開支會大左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2ddee40a969d9f618eb961919fb1e9590587ceb9","tid":102831,"uid":36049,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-06T14:08:27.000Z","msg":"搵5皮表示同搵兩皮既生活冇乜分別<br />\n相反有冇父幹分別先差別大"},{"pid":"6a8a8e0c2a2b5abbd50a6105788a31039e21ec1e","tid":102831,"uid":67280,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-06T14:10:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>可能工時12個鍾以上呢</blockquote><br />\n抵屌啦，用一個月等於人地一年，當你做2年已經等於人地基層20年，有咩蝕<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n好天打定落雨柴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"67841d028b8d7bb36bc9ec2f55ad1e9e080f0e01","tid":102831,"uid":35857,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-06T14:10:18.000Z","msg":"十皮一個月真係做皇帝<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c72ac29d6b7fa1c9b323f06b561b8a5f04d6425c","tid":102831,"uid":67280,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-06T14:14:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>成班撚樣根本唔知10皮一個月份工會點？9 hea行行企企 等出糧？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n咁你又唔講，但又屌你吹水，你果十皮係咪都係吹出黎咋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bf8cb221b6aa2ae4df7ebb679b4f785da00e5da2","tid":102831,"uid":67280,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-06T14:15:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>成班撚樣根本唔知10皮一個月份工會點？9 hea行行企企 等出糧？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n咁你又唔講，但又屌人吹水，你果十皮係咪都係吹出黎咋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"18accae99876eb00a7c9416bfa8cadc8f7d4c823","tid":102831,"uid":54827,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-06T14:15:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>成班撚樣根本唔知10皮一個月份工會點？9 hea行行企企 等出糧？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nOn9跟本就係你自己係度ff搵十萬會好撚辛苦做到狗咁，可能真係咩都要理，但實際上咪又係點人做野，做到個啲位跟本冇邊幾個管到你"}]}